# Steps to install erlang on standard debian

1) add user to "sudoers" file
   - edit /etc/sudoers
   - add <user>  ALL=(ALL) ALL

2) sudo apt-get install gcc

3) sudo apt-get install libssl-dev

4) wget http://www.erlang.org/download/otp_src_R15B01.tar.gz

5) tar xz otp_src_R15B01.tar.gz

6) cd otp_src_R15B01

7) export LANG=C

8) sudo ./configure

9) sudo make

10) sudo make install